headline: Agoda Strengthens Flights Offering with Amadeus Partnership in Asia Pacific
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda announces a strategic partnership with Amadeus, a global provider of travel technology solutions, to make it even easier for Agoda customers to find the best priced flight while giving them access to a wider range of targeted airline content. The initiative will start in Thailand before rolling out across the wider Asian region.
